  "contentHtml": "\n                                    \n\n                                                                            <p><img src=\"https://health.economictimes.indiatimes.com/Themes/Release/theme4/images/icons/et-default-user.svg\" alt=\"Online Bureau\">\n                                            \n                                        </p>\n                                                                        \n                                                                                    <ul>\n                                                                                                    <li>\n                                                                                                                    <a>Online Bureau</a>\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                                                                        \n                                                                                                            </li>\n                                                                                                                                                    <li><a href=\"/agency/88675629/ETHealthWorld\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ETHealthWorld</a></li>\n                                                                                            </ul>\n                                                                                <ul>\n                                                                                            <li>Published On Apr 27, 2026 at 12:24 PM IST</li>\n                                                                                                                                </ul>\n                                    \n                                                                            \n                                                                        \n                                \n                                \n\n                    <!-- Display video article in news article for the custom next story -->\n                    \n                    <!-- Modifying the body placing embeds,promoslots,related etc.-->\n                                        <figure><img src=\"/images/default.jpg\" alt=\"\"></figure><p>New Delhi: <a href=\"/tag/nathealth\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">NATHEALTH</a>, an apex body representing the <a href=\"/tag/indian+healthcare+industry\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Indian healthcare industry</a>, has expanded its leadership team for FY 2026–27 with the appointment of <a href=\"/tag/shankha+banerjee\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Shankha Banerjee</a>, CEO, Dr. Lal PathLabs, as Treasurer and Mandeep Singh Kumar, Managing Director and Vice President, Medtronic India, as Secretary.The appointments were announced following the organisation’s Governing Council meeting and add to the previously announced leadership team headed by Sangita Reddy, Joint Managing Director, Apollo Hospitals, who serves as President.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>With the new additions, the expanded leadership team includes Sangita Reddy as President, Himanshu Baid as Senior Vice President, Varun Khanna as Vice President, along with <a href=\"/tag/shankha+banerjee\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Shankha Banerjee</a> as Treasurer and Mandeep Singh Kumar as Secretary.</p>\n                            <p>Advt\n                            </p>\n\n                              \n                                                         \n                        <p>Siddhartha Bhattacharya will continue as Secretary General of <a href=\"/tag/nathealth\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">NATHEALTH</a>, leading the Secretariat’s efforts to strengthen strategic partnerships, expand regional stakeholder engagement, and collaborate with policymakers to drive the next phase of healthcare development in India.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>\"The inclusion of leaders from diagnostics and medical technology would strengthen the organisation’s ability to drive systemic change across the healthcare ecosystem. She noted that as India progresses towards the vision of Viksit Bharat 2047, leadership with a comprehensive understanding of the continuum of care will be crucial to building a system focused on prevention, patient safety, and long-term wellbeing,\" Reddy said.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>Speaking on his appointment, Banerjee emphasised the growing importance of early intervention, continuity of care, and data-driven decision-making in addressing the rising burden of non-communicable diseases. He highlighted that diagnostics will play a critical role in enabling early detection and guiding clinical decisions as India shifts toward more <a href=\"/tag/preventive+healthcare\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">preventive healthcare</a>.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M --><p>\"India’s healthcare ecosystem is at a pivotal moment, driven by increasing demand, evolving patient expectations, and rapid innovation. He added that strengthening infrastructure, improving clinical outcomes, and fostering collaboration across government, industry, and care providers will be key to building a future-ready healthcare system,\" Kumar added.</p><!-- PROMOSLOT_M -->\n                            <p>Advt\n                            </p>\n\n                              \n                                                         \n                        <p>With the strengthened leadership team, NATHEALTH said it aims to play a greater role in shaping India’s <a href=\"/tag/healthcare+transformation\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">healthcare transformation</a> through innovation, stronger health systems, and enhanced public–private collaboration.                    </p><!-- Category Most Read Placement -->\n                                                                    \n                                                                \n                                <ul>\n                                                                            <!-- <li>By <span>Online Bureau</span>,</li> -->\n                                    \n\n                                                                            <li>By\n                                                                                            <a>Online Bureau</a>\n\n                                                                                                                                                                                        , \n                                                                                    </li>\n                                                                        <li><a href=\"/agency/88675629/ETHealthWorld\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">ETHealthWorld</a></li>\n                                </ul>\n                                <ul>\n                                    <!-- <li> Updated On Apr 27, 2026 at 12:24 PM IST</li> -->\n                                    <li>Published On Apr 27, 2026 at 12:24 PM IST</li>\n                                    <!-- <li class=\"desktop-view\">2 min read</li> -->\n                                </ul>\n                            \n                                        \n\n                    \n\n                    <!-- Comment Section -->\n                                            \n                                        <!-- Comment Section -->\n\n                    \n                      \n    \n            <p>\n                </p><h2>Join the community of 2M+ industry professionals. </h2>   \n                <h3>Subscribe to Newsletter to get latest insights &amp; analysis in your inbox.</h3>\n            <p></p>\n\n            <!-- <figure class=\"